  "thag2.32:1.1": "Inconstant little houses:",
  "thag2.32:1.2": "now here, now there, again & again,",
  "thag2.32:1.3": "I sought the house-builder.",
  "thag2.32:1.4": "Painful is birth, again & again.",
  "thag2.32:2.1": "House-builder, you’re seen!",
  "thag2.32:2.2": "You will not build a house again.",
  "thag2.32:2.3": "All your rafters are broken,",
  "thag2.32:2.4": "and your gables torn down.",
  "thag2.32:2.5": "Released from restriction, the mind",
  "thag2.32:2.6": "will be blown out right here.",
